{"tid":473134,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳Apple密謀新一代iPhone　支持雙卡雙待 (23:31)","createTime":"2017-11-19T02:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T15:31:31.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"bb426f6322c8c604a6f405af5d54f56c29aece4c","tid":473134,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T02:26:36.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=2zDovFNkhUfj3xsUiTQ1FNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e022917c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】外媒報道，蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)與高通的關係愈來愈差，後者高昂且不合理的專利費，是關係變差的主因。<br />\n<br />\n對於蘋果公司來說，縮減高通基帶在iPhone中的佔比，是他們目前正在做一件事，而Intel趁機上位就成為了可能，而他們剛剛發布了新一代的基帶。<br />\n<br />\nIntel昨天發布的是XMM 7560基帶，其整體實力跟高通的X20基本保持一致，都支持4x4 MIMO天線技術，LTE傳輸速度會有明顯提升，相比當前iPhone使用的基帶晶片。<br />\n<br />\n多次準確預測蘋果新品的凱基證券分析師郭明池表示，明年的iPhone將會使用Intel的XMM 7560（現在是XMM 7480），他還強調，新一代iPhone還要支持雙卡雙待，只使用一套晶片就可同時使用兩張SIM卡。<br />\n<br />\n郭明池並表示，iPhone明年將有三款新品推出，其中一款必然支持雙卡雙待（從產品定位來看，極有可能是iPhone X升級版），同時還支持LTE+LTE網絡連接，如果真是這樣的話，那麼內地果粉購買iPhone的熱情會更高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171118/20171118233136fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20171118%2F20171118233136fi.html&d=2zDovFNkhUfj3xsUiTQ1FNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=95a99488\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20171118/20171118233136fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"9fcd1cd7e63608860185f39d70f9885d66fc19de","tid":473134,"uid":26200,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T02:42:23.000Z","msg":"iphone x 機身迫到咁重放到雙卡?<br />\n下年唔cut sim轉esim都偷笑"},{"pid":"2dc02e0176586acaa11b687cabe39ab28fde9265","tid":473134,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T02:52:32.000Z","msg":"咁算唔算新發明"},{"pid":"850951fa4be5b7fbc4f96f0912d6d38cf7e5b21b","tid":473134,"uid":5686,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>iphone x 機身迫到咁重放到雙卡?<br />\n下年唔cut sim轉esim都偷笑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCut完到變E-SIM 又可以雙卡的話，可樂而不為呢？"},{"pid":"31aa260ce51a7b87e5b04ac15f6c2f8fd692bf0d","tid":473134,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁算唔算新發明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nApple 10樣9樣都唔係新發明"},{"pid":"64cda28edf8567e2ed6be16aacf72abfb729d97c","tid":473134,"uid":52068,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T04:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁算唔算新發明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nApple 10樣9樣都唔係新發明</blockquote><br />\n去到apple 改個名就會變成new features<br />\n重新定義"},{"pid":"339fe22b3596117b2c0cb230c6668da407d3ee03","tid":473134,"uid":39527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁算唔算新發明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nApple 10樣9樣都唔係新發明</blockquote><br />\n去到apple 改個名就會變成new features<br />\n重新定義</blockquote><br />\n比個勁d既名佢就係新發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed7890f852d6bea19a9d6c7c80c7346de0d938ac","tid":473134,"uid":48907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁算唔算新發明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nApple 10樣9樣都唔係新發明</blockquote><br />\n去到apple 改個名就會變成new features<br />\n重新定義</blockquote><br />\n比個勁d既名佢就係新發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\niSim"},{"pid":"788863d1ece7e2e74c20411cdc4673aeed97bdf6","tid":473134,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁算唔算新發明</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nApple 10樣9樣都唔係新發明</blockquote><br />\n去到apple 改個名就會變成new features<br />\n重新定義</blockquote><br />\n比個勁d既名佢就係新發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/no